<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Redis Sampling Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .status-badge { width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; margin-right: 12px; vertical-align: middle; }
        .bg-up { background-color: #28a745; box-shadow: 0 0 10px #28a745; }
        .bg-down { background-color: #dc3545; box-shadow: 0 0 10px #dc3545; }
        .card { border-radius: 15px; overflow: hidden; }
        .card-header { border-bottom: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <div class="card shadow-lg">
                    <div class="card-header bg-dark text-white text-center py-4">
                        <h2 class="mb-0">Redis Sampling Labs</h2>
                        <p class="text-white-50 mb-0">Phase 1: Basic & Caching Infrastructure</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body p-5">
                        <div class="text-center mb-5">
                            <h4 class="fw-bold text-secondary">System Monitoring</h4>
                            <p class="text-muted">실시간으로 Redis 인프라의 가동 상태를 확인합니다.</p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Redis Status Section -->
                        <div class="p-4 rounded-4 bg-white border {{#isRedisUp}}border-success{{/isRedisUp}}{{^isRedisUp}}border-danger{{/isRedisUp}} shadow-sm mb-4">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                    <span class="status-badge {{#isRedisUp}}bg-up{{/isRedisUp}}{{^isRedisUp}}bg-down{{/isRedisUp}}"></span>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="mb-0 fw-bold {{#isRedisUp}}text-success{{/isRedisUp}}{{^isRedisUp}}text-danger{{/isRedisUp}}">
                                            Redis Engine Status
                                        </h5>
                                        <small class="text-muted">Component: health.redis</small>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-end">
                                    <span class="badge {{#isRedisUp}}bg-success{{/isRedisUp}}{{^isRedisUp}}bg-danger{{/isRedisUp}} fs-6 px-3">
                                        {{redisStatus}}
                                    }</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <hr class="my-3 opacity-10">
                            <p class="mb-0 {{#isRedisUp}}text-dark{{/isRedisUp}}{{^isRedisUp}}text-danger fw-bold{{/isRedisUp}}">
                                {{#isRedisUp}}
                                    ✅ 로컬 또는 컨테이너에서 구동 중인 Redis 서버에 성공적으로 연결되었습니다.
                                {{/isRedisUp}}
                                {{^isRedisUp}}
                                    ❌ Redis 서버와의 연결이 끊겼습니다. `redis-server` 구동 여부를 확인해주세요.
                                {{/isRedisUp}}
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg py-3">
                                <i class="bi bi-arrow-clockwise"></i> Refresh Status
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer bg-white text-center py-3 border-top-0">
                        <small class="text-muted">Developer Session: {{git_user_name}}</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
